<p><span className="vocab">山嵐<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>山嵐</rb><rt>やまあらし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yama Arashi (nickname for Hotta, the head mathematics teacher)</span></span>はいよいよ<span className="vocab">辞表<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>辞表</rb><rt>じひょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;letter of resignation</span></span>を<span className="vocab">出して<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>だ</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;submitted; presented</span></span>、<span className="vocab">職員<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>職員</rb><rt>しょくいん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;staff</span></span><span className="vocab">一同<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一同</rb><rt>いちどう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one and all</span></span>に<span className="vocab">告別<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>告別</rb><rt>こくべつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;farewell; parting</span></span>の<span className="vocab">挨拶<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>挨拶</rb><rt>あいさつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;civilities; formalities</span></span>をして<span className="vocab">浜<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>浜</rb><rt>はま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;beach; shore</span></span>の<span className="vocab">港屋<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>港屋</rb><rt>みなとや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Minatoya (name of an inn)</span></span>まで<span className="vocab">下った<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>下</rb><rt>さが</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;went down (to)</span></span>が、<span className="vocab">人<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人</rb><rt>ひと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;people</span></span>に<span className="vocab">知れない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>知</rb><rt>し</rt></ruby>れない&nbsp;unbeknownst</span></span>ように<span className="vocab">引き返して<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>引</rb><rt>ひ</rt></ruby>き<ruby><rb>返</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;doubled back</span></span>、<span className="vocab">温泉<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>温泉</rb><rt>ゆ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;baths; hot springs</span></span>の<span className="vocab">町<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>町</rb><rt>まち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;town</span></span>の<span className="vocab">枡屋<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>枡屋</rb><rt>ますや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Masuya (name of an inn)</span></span>の<span className="vocab">表<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>表</rb><rt>おもて</rt></ruby>&nbsp;front side; street side</span></span><span className="vocab">二階<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>二階</rb><rt>にかい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;second floor</span></span>へ<span className="vocab">潜んで<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>潜</rb><rt>ひそ</rt></ruby>んで&nbsp;lurk; lie low</span></span>、<span className="vocab">障子<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>障子</rb><rt>しょうじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;shōji (sliding paper screen)</span></span>へ<span className="vocab">穴<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>穴</rb><rt>あな</rt></ruby>&nbsp;hole</span></span>をあけて<span className="vocab">覗き出した<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>覗</rb><rt>のぞ</rt></ruby>き<ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>だ</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;began surveillance</span></span>。これを知ってるものはおればかりだろう。<span className="vocab">赤シャツ<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>赤</rb><rt>あか</rt></ruby>シャツ&nbsp;Red Shirt (nickname for the head teacher)</span></span>が<span className="vocab">忍んで来れば<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>忍</rb><rt>しの</rt></ruby>んで<ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>れば&nbsp;come sneaking</span></span>どうせ<span className="vocab">夜<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>夜</rb><rt>よる</rt></ruby>&nbsp;night</span></span>だ。しかも<span className="vocab">宵の口<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>宵</rb><rt>よい</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>口</rb><rt>くち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;early evening</span></span>は<span className="vocab">生徒<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生徒</rb><rt>せいと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;students</span></span>やその<span className="vocab">他<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>他</rb><rt>ほか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;other</span></span>の<span className="vocab">目<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>目</rb><rt>め</rt></ruby>&nbsp;eyes</span></span>があるから、<span className="vocab">少なくとも<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>少</rb><rt>すく</rt></ruby>なくとも&nbsp;at least</span></span><span className="vocab">九時<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>九時</rb><rt>くじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;nine (o'clock)</span></span><span className="vocab">過ぎ<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>過</rb><rt>す</rt></ruby>ぎ&nbsp;after; past</span></span><span className="vocab">に極ってる<span className="vocabdef">に<ruby><rb>極</rb><rt>きま</rt></ruby>ってる&nbsp;is certain; is a given</span></span>。<span className="vocab">最初<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>最初</rb><rt>さいしょ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;initial; first</span></span>の<span className="vocab">二晩<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>二晩</rb><rt>ふたばん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;two nights</span></span>はおれも<span className="vocab">十一時<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>十一時</rb><rt>じゅういちじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;eleven (o'clock)</span></span><span className="vocab">頃<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>頃</rb><rt>ごろ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;about; around</span></span>まで<span className="vocab">張番<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>張番</rb><rt>はりばん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;lookout; watch</span></span>をしたが、赤シャツの<span className="vocab">影<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>影</rb><rt>かげ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;shadow; sign (of something)</span></span>も<span className="vocab">見えない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>えない&nbsp;could not be seen</span></span>。<span className="vocab">三日目<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>三日目</rb><rt>みっかめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;third day</span></span>には九時から<span className="vocab">十時半<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>十時半</rb><rt>じゅうじはん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;ten thirty</span></span>まで覗いたがやはり<span className="vocab">駄目<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>駄目</rb><rt>だめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;unsuccessful; no good</span></span>だ。駄目を<span className="vocab">踏んで<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>踏</rb><rt>ふ</rt></ruby>んで&nbsp;go through; complete</span></span><span className="vocab">夜なか<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>夜</rb><rt>よ</rt></ruby>なか&nbsp;late at night; middle of the night</span></span>に<span className="vocab">下宿<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>下宿</rb><rt>げしゅく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;lodgings</span></span>へ<span className="vocab">帰る<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>帰</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;return home</span></span>ほど<span className="vocab">馬鹿気た<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>馬鹿気</rb><rt>ばかげ</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;foolish; idiotic</span></span><span className="vocab">事<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;act; thing</span></span>はない。<span className="vocab">四五日<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>四五日</rb><rt>しごんち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;four or five days</span></span>すると、うちの<span className="vocab">婆さん<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>婆</rb><rt>ばあ</rt></ruby>さん&nbsp;old woman</span></span>が<span className="vocab">少々<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>少々</rb><rt>しょうしょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a bit; somewhat</span></span><span className="vocab">心配<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心配</rb><rt>しんぱい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;worry; concern</span></span>を<span className="vocab">始めて<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>始</rb><rt>はじ</rt></ruby>めて&nbsp;began; started</span></span>、<span className="vocab">奥さん<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>奥</rb><rt>おく</rt></ruby>さん&nbsp;wife</span></span>のおありるのに、<span className="vocab">夜遊び<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>夜遊</rb><rt>よあそ</rt></ruby>び&nbsp;nightlife</span></span>はおやめたがええぞなもしと<span className="vocab">忠告した<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>忠告</rb><rt>ちゅうこく</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;admonished; cautioned</span></span>。そんな夜遊びとは夜遊びが<span className="vocab">違う<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>違</rb><rt>ちが</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;be different (from)</span></span>。こっちのは<span className="vocab">天に代って<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>天</rb><rt>てん</rt></ruby>に<ruby><rb>代</rb><rt>かわ</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;on behalf of Heaven</span></span><span className="vocab">誅戮を加える<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>誅戮</rb><rt>ちゅうりく</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>加</rb><rt>くわ</rt></ruby>える&nbsp;administer punishment</span></span>夜遊びだ。とはいうものの<span className="vocab">一週間<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一週間</rb><rt>いっしゅうかん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one week</span></span>も<span className="vocab">通って<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>通</rb><rt>かよ</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;attend; frequent</span></span>、<span className="vocab">少しも<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>少</rb><rt>すこ</rt></ruby>しも&nbsp;(not) in the least</span></span><span className="vocab">験が見えない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>験</rb><rt>げん</rt></ruby>が<ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>えない&nbsp;produce no results</span></span>と、いやになるもんだ。おれは<span className="vocab">性急な<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>性急</rb><rt>せっかち</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;impatient</span></span><span className="vocab">性分<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>性分</rb><rt>しょうぶん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;nature; disposition</span></span>だから、<span className="vocab">熱心<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>熱心</rb><rt>ねっしん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fervent; ardent</span></span>になると<span className="vocab">徹夜<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>徹夜</rb><rt>てつや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;all-nighter</span></span>でもして<span className="vocab">仕事<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>仕事</rb><rt>しごと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;work; task</span></span>をするが、<span className="vocab">その代り<span className="vocabdef">その<ruby><rb>代</rb><rt>かわ</rt></ruby>り&nbsp;on the other hand</span></span><span className="vocab">何によらず<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なん</rt></ruby>によらず&nbsp;with no task at hand</span></span><span className="vocab">長持ちのした<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>長持</rb><rt>ながも</rt></ruby>ちのした&nbsp;endured</span></span><span className="vocab">試し<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>試</rb><rt>ため</rt></ruby>し&nbsp;instance; example</span></span>がない。いかに<span className="vocab">天誅<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>天誅</rb><rt>てんちゅう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;divine justice</span></span><span className="vocab">党<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>党</rb><rt>とう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;party; faction</span></span>でも<span className="vocab">飽きる<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>飽</rb><rt>あ</rt></ruby>きる&nbsp;grow weary (of)</span></span>事に<span className="vocab">変りはない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>変</rb><rt>かわ</rt></ruby>りはない&nbsp;is the same as always</span></span>。<span className="vocab">六日目<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>六日目</rb><rt>むいかめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sixth day</span></span>には少々いやになって、<span className="vocab">七日目<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>七日目</rb><rt>なのかめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;seventh day</span></span>にはもう<span className="vocab">休もう<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>休</rb><rt>やす</rt></ruby>もう&nbsp;give it a rest; call it quits</span></span>かと<span className="vocab">思った<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;thought (of doing)</span></span>。そこへ<span className="vocab">行く<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;go (to)</span></span>と山嵐は<span className="vocab">頑固<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>頑固</rb><rt>がんこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;stubborn; obstinate</span></span>なものだ。宵から<span className="vocab">十二時<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>十二時</rb><rt>じゅうにじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;midnight</span></span><span className="vocab">過<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>過</rb><rt>すぎ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;after; past</span></span>までは<span className="vocab">眼<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>眼</rb><rt>まなこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;eye</span></span>を障子へつけて、<span className="vocab">角屋<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>角屋</rb><rt>かどや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Kadoya (name of an inn / restaurant)</span></span>の<span className="vocab">丸ぼや<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>丸</rb><rt>まる</rt></ruby>ぼや&nbsp;spherical (fire)</span></span>の<span className="vocab">瓦斯燈<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>瓦斯燈</rb><rt>がすとう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;gas lamp</span></span>の<span className="vocab">下<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>下</rb><rt>した</rt></ruby>&nbsp;below; beneath</span></span>を<span className="vocab">睨めっきり<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>睨</rb><rt>にら</rt></ruby>めっきり&nbsp;watch intently</span></span>である。おれが行くと<span className="vocab">今日<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今日</rb><rt>きょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;today</span></span>は<span className="vocab">何人<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何人</rb><rt>なんにん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;how many people</span></span><span className="vocab">客<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>客</rb><rt>きゃく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;patrons</span></span>があって、<span className="vocab">泊り<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>泊</rb><rt>とま</rt></ruby>り&nbsp;staying the night</span></span>が何人、<span className="vocab">女<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>女</rb><rt>おんな</rt></ruby>&nbsp;women</span></span>が何人といろいろな<span className="vocab">統計<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>統計</rb><rt>とうけい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;figures; statistics</span></span>を<span className="vocab">示す<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>示</rb><rt>しめ</rt></ruby>す&nbsp;indicate; point out</span></span>のには<span className="vocab">驚ろいた<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>驚</rb><rt>おど</rt></ruby>ろいた&nbsp;be surprised; be impressed</span></span>。どうも<span className="vocab">来ない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>こ</rt></ruby>ない&nbsp;not show</span></span>ようじゃないかと<span className="vocab">云う<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;said; remarked</span></span>と、うん、たしかに<span className="vocab">来る<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;show up</span></span>はずだがと<span className="vocab">時々<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>時々</rb><rt>ときどき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sometimes</span></span><span className="vocab">腕組をして<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>腕組</rb><rt>うでぐみ</rt></ruby>をして&nbsp;fold one's arms (across one's chest)</span></span><span className="vocab">溜息をつく<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>溜息</rb><rt>ためいき</rt></ruby>をつく&nbsp;release a sigh</span></span>。<span className="vocab">可愛想に<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>可愛想</rb><rt>かわいそう</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;sadly; pitiably</span></span>、もし赤シャツがここへ<span className="vocab">一度<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一度</rb><rt>いちど</rt></ruby>&nbsp;once</span></span><span className="vocab">来て<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>て&nbsp;show up; come</span></span>くれなければ、山嵐は、<span className="vocab">生涯<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生涯</rb><rt>しょうがい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;as long as one lives</span></span>天誅を加える事は<span className="vocab">出来ない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出来</rb><rt>でき</rt></ruby>ない&nbsp;cannot accomplish</span></span>のである。</p>

